title: RHOBH Furs & Flip-Flops
itunes:title: RHOBH Furs & Flip-Flops
description:
Danny recaps The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the rest of Garcelle's party, where Erika got out of hand, plus Sutton got more into it with Room 23's Diana Jenkins as Kyle The Splits Richards inserted herself. After Garcelle's party, Sutton throws a salad soiree at her unfinished home in the mud. Danny also touches on episode 4 of The Real Housewives Ultimate Girls Trip (more to come on that next week)!
